nba_game.name: nba_game
nba_game.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_game (-- table for NBA game information
    home_team_id bigint, -- ID of the home team
    attendance bigint, -- number of people in attendance
    sellout bigint, -- whether the game was a sellout or not
    period bigint, -- current period of the game
    game_clock bigint, -- current game clock time
    game_time_utc timestamp with time zone, -- game time in UTC
    game_et timestamp with time zone, -- game time in ET
    away_team_id bigint, -- ID of the away team
    series_text text, -- text description of the series
    game_code text, -- code for the game
    duration text, -- duration of the game
    series_game_number text, -- number of the game in the series
    game_id text -- ID of the game
);

nba_play_by_play.name: nba_play_by_play
nba_play_by_play.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_play_by_play (-- play by play data for NBA games
    score_away bigint, -- score of the away team after the play
    points_total bigint, -- total points scored after the play
    person_id bigint, -- ID of the person involved in the play
    period bigint, -- period of the game when the play occurred
    team_id bigint, -- ID of the team involved in the play
    x_legacy bigint, -- legacy x-coordinate of the play
    video_available bigint, -- flag indicating if video is available for the play
    action_id bigint, -- ID of the action in the play
    action_number bigint, -- number of the action in the play
    y_legacy bigint, -- legacy y-coordinate of the play
    shot_distance bigint, -- distance of the shot in the play
    clock bigint, -- time on the game clock when the play occurred
    is_field_goal bigint, -- flag indicating if the play is a field goal
    score_home bigint, -- score of the home team after the play
    game_id text, -- ID of the game
    team_tricode text, -- tricode of the team involved in the play
    shot_result text, -- result of the shot in the play
    location text, -- location of the play
    description text, -- description of the play
    action_type text, -- type of the action in the play
    sub_type text -- sub-type of the action in the play
);

nba_player.name: nba_player
nba_player.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_player (-- table for NBA players to sync multiple versions of the player to the same player id
    team_id bigint, -- ID of the team the player belongs to
    person_id bigint, -- ID of the player (there can be multiple rows)
    status text, -- player's status
    family_name text, -- player's last name
    first_name text, -- player's first name
    jersey_num text, -- player's jersey number
    name_i text, -- player's name abbreviation
    position text, -- player's position
    name text -- player's full name
);

nba_player_game_stats.name: nba_player_game_stats
nba_player_game_stats.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_player_game_stats (-- table for storing game stats of NBA players
    plus_minus_points bigint, -- plus/minus points of the player in the game
    team_id bigint, -- id of the team the player belongs to
    person_id bigint, -- id of the player
    fouls_personal bigint, -- number of personal fouls committed by the player
    points bigint, -- total points scored by the player in the game
    field_goals_made bigint, -- number of field goals made by the player
    field_goals_attempted bigint, -- number of field goals attempted by the player
    field_goals_percentage double precision, -- percentage of field goals made by the player
    three_pointers_made bigint, -- number of three pointers made by the player
    three_pointers_attempted bigint, -- number of three pointers attempted by the player
    three_pointers_percentage double precision, -- percentage of three pointers made by the player
    free_throws_made bigint, -- number of free throws made by the player
    free_throws_attempted bigint, -- number of free throws attempted by the player
    free_throws_percentage double precision, -- percentage of free throws made by the player
    rebounds_offensive bigint, -- number of offensive rebounds by the player
    rebounds_defensive bigint, -- number of defensive rebounds by the player
    rebounds_total bigint, -- total number of rebounds by the player
    assists bigint, -- number of assists made by the player
    steals bigint, -- number of steals made by the player
    blocks bigint, -- number of blocks made by the player
    turnovers bigint, -- number of turnovers committed by the player
    minutes text, -- total minutes played by the player in the game
    game_id text --foreign key
);

nba_player_roster.name: nba_player_roster
nba_player_roster.schema:
CREATE TABLE nba_player_roster (-- NBA player roster information
    person_id bigint, -- unique identifier for each player
    season_exp bigint, -- number of seasons of experience in the NBA
    team_id bigint, -- unique identifier for the team the player is currently playing for
    from_year bigint, -- year the player started playing in the NBA
    to_year bigint, -- year the player ended playing in the NBA
    school text, -- name of the school the player attended
    country text, -- country the player is from
    last_affiliation text, -- last affiliation of the player before joining the NBA
    height text, -- height of the player in feet-inches format
    weight text, -- weight of the player in pounds
    draft_year text, -- year the player was drafted
    jersey text, -- jersey number of the player
    position text, -- position the player plays in
    roster_status text, -- status of the player in the team's roster
    draft_round text, -- round the player was drafted in
    draft_number text, -- number the player was drafted at
    seasons text, -- list of seasons the player played in the NBA
    first_name text, -- first name of the player
    last_name text, -- last name of the player
    name_i text, -- abbreviated name of the player
    birth_date text -- date of birth of the player
);

    player_blk_leader_blk bigint, -- number of blocks by the player who led the team in blocks

    field_goals_attempted bigint, -- number of field goals attempted by the team
    field_goals_percentage double precision, -- percentage of field goals made by the team
    three_pointers_made bigint, -- number of three pointers made by the team
    three_pointers_attempted bigint, -- number of three pointers attempted by the team
    three_pointers_percentage double precision, -- percentage of three pointers made by the team
    free_throws_made bigint, -- number of free throws made by the team
    free_throws_attempted bigint, -- number of free throws attempted by the team
    free_throws_percentage double precision, -- percentage of free throws made by the team

    rebounds_defensive bigint, -- number of defensive rebounds by the team
